    {
      "id": "legend-notes",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1440,
      "width": 1400,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "GPU = /dev/dri mount for Intel/AMD hardware acceleration    |    docker.sock = Docker socket access for container management\nhost net = network_mode: host (bypasses Docker networking)    |    proxynet = all services share this external Docker bridge network\nAll Traefik routed services use *.${TRAEFIK_BASE_DOMAIN} with Let's Encrypt TLS via CloudNS DNS challenge",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
