      "originalText": "GPU = /dev/dri mount for Intel/AMD hardware acceleration    |    docker.sock = Docker socket access for container management\nhost net = network_mode: host (bypasses Docker networking)    |    proxynet = all services share this external Docker bridge network\nAll Traefik routed services use *.${TRAEFIK_BASE_DOMAIN} with Let's Encrypt TLS via CloudNS DNS challenge",
